{"lastModified":1752854878486,"uri":"c::7819143053::vessel::77945888-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60","yachtType":["Sailing","Gulet"],"description":"Operating Area: Turkey\n\nNORTH WIND is a 44.00m / 144ft Luxury Gulet Superyacht built in 2023 by Custom. Sleeping 10 guests in 5 cabins and with a crew of 8. Cruising at 11.00 kn/ph with a top speed of 15.00 kn/ph. The guest cabins comprise a Master cabin with a king size bed and en-suite bathroom facilities, 3 double cabins with queen size beds and en-suite bathroom facilities and a twin cabin with a twin bed and en-suite bathroom facilities. She has a huge swimming platform and a very confortable flybridge.","blueprint":{"name":"NORTH WIND","images":["/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::77945888-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::fcf29ea0-2961-11ef-b2e5-c5e14ecf6a1b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::77945888-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::ea216b80-2961-11ef-b2e5-c5e14ecf6a1b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::77945888-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::6a5d05f0-c997-11ee-aa69-e7a634efe9ad.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::77945888-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::11b67a00-2962-11ef-b2e5-c5e14ecf6a1b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::77945888-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::11b58fa0-2962-11ef-b2e5-c5e14ecf6a1b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::77945888-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::11b604d0-2962-11ef-b2e5-c5e14ecf6a1b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::77945888-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::11b62be0-2962-11ef-b2e5-c5e14ecf6a1b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::77945888-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::843515a0-2962-11ef-b2e5-c5e14ecf6a1b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::77945888-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::84360000-296